Big Brother Naija, BBNaija 2020 winner, Laycon has revealed plans for some housemates who participated in the reality show. Laycon during his media tour said he would feature some of the housemates on this ‘Hip Hop video song. He said this to Nengi, Vee and Neo in a live interview on Friday. He also stated that he intends to give back to the society. According to him, ”it is not about winning the show alone but about winning in life. ”People have shown me love and support so it is time to give back.” Laycon walked away with N85 million Naira worth of grand prize on Sunday.